              "body": "`stagedWriteCache` fsyncs the temp file but does not fsync the directory after `Rename`. If the intent is the same crash-safety/durability guarantee as `fsroot.Root.StagedWrite`, consider syncing the directory handle (best-effort) after the rename so the audit entry is durable across a power loss/crash.",
